de.thkoeln.bibl.api.rfid.tag.data

Class TagData

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.thkoeln.bibl.api.rfid.tag.data.TagData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DDMData

    public class TagData
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class represents the data of a tag and implements methods to manipulate this data. Sub-classes can use this functionality and extend is by their specific implementation. Instances of this class and sub-classes implicitly support XML serializing by JAXB.
    Author:
    Patrick Rogalla TODO add writing support for tag data and ddm/bibliotheca data model
